short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension calls Nicolás Maduro's regime for what it is: a dictatorship.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Every mention of Nicolás Maduro will be replaced by "Venezuelan Dictator Nicolás Maduro".
Every mention of him winning an "election" will be changed to point out it's a sham election.
Every public figure who has used their position to whitewash the Venezuelan Dictatorship will also be pointed out as such.

The whitewashing of Nicolás Maduro's regime ends today.
